op playlist of action-packed events. Whether it’s competing for the best starting position, the ultimate jump, or finishing first place, if there’s something to do, there’s someone to beat. Any Speed Points earned on Wii U will add to your existing total if you are playing the game on any of the other available platforms through CloudCompete."	//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co20a6.jpg	2013-03-14 00:00:00+00	E10	21699
